091EA8DD.Line13.6D03F: Yes, and without Elias, we may have more success against Lilith. Where do we start?

8E02627B.Line5.789BF: Seek out Timue in the marshes. She traded with the power in the swamp and received long life. She may have the answer to killing Elias for good.

A313225F.Line15.6D03F: Neyrelle and I will start looking for her.
